Edit: after changing the contents of  `/usr/share/containers/oci/hooks.d/oci-nvidia-hook.json` to what's currently at 
`https://github.com/NVIDIA/nvidia-container-toolkit/blob/main/oci-nvidia-hook.json` the bug is solved. The gpu is not used nevertheless, but the hook now "matches". Contents:

```
{
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "hook": {
        "path": "/usr/bin/nvidia-container-runtime-hook",
        "args": ["nvidia-container-runtime-hook", "prestart"],
        "env": [
            "PATH=/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin"
        ]
    },
    "when": {
        "always": true,
	"commands": [".*"]
    },
    "stages": ["prestart"]
}
```
